<div class="nbunit" id="a3Sep1938"><font color="red">3 September 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Faber and Faber to Paul L&eacute;on):   We did send the musical quotation proof to Mr Pendleton and he has already corrected it and sent it back to us. </div>
